<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 08:11:22 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>澳大利亚制裁参与西岸针对巴勒斯坦人的暴力行为的七名以色列定居者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/australia-sanctions-seven-israelis-involved-in-west-bank-violence-against-palestinians/00000190-e8ba-d469-a39d-ecbfc0310000</link><description>澳大利亚的声明称，一些以色列人参与了性侵犯和性虐待。制裁还针对“山顶青年”，此举将使未来能够对参与袭击巴勒斯坦人的非法前哨定居者采取更广泛的行动</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 07:57:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/australia-sanctions-seven-israelis-involved-in-west-bank-violence-against-palestinians/00000190-e8ba-d469-a39d-ecbfc0310000</guid></item><item><title>全文：内塔尼亚胡 2024 年向国会发表的讲话</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/full-text-netanyahus-2024-address-to-congress/00000190-e6c0-d469-a39d-e6d7117d0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 07:34:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/full-text-netanyahus-2024-address-to-congress/00000190-e6c0-d469-a39d-e6d7117d0000</guid></item><item><title>如果加沙没有最终结果并脱离现实，内塔尼亚胡的雄辩无法赢得对以色列的支持</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/without-a-gaza-endgame-netanyahus-eloquence-wont-translate-into-support-for-israel/00000190-e688-db2f-a3b3-fefec4ad0000</link><description>如果内塔尼亚胡声称人质的命运如此紧迫，他就不会再次推迟卡塔尔谈判的恢复；与总理关系密切的人士称他的讲话具有历史意义，但以色列人专注于救回人质，而美国人则专注于选举</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 03:03:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/without-a-gaza-endgame-netanyahus-eloquence-wont-translate-into-support-for-israel/00000190-e688-db2f-a3b3-fefec4ad0000</guid></item><item><title>三名以色列人在约旦河西岸疑似驾车枪击事件中受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article-live/gaza-truce-talks-in-closing-stages-senior-u-s-official-says-israeli-source-gaps-remain/00000190-e7ae-d469-a39d-e7bfcb150000</link><description>以色列国防军找到了 10 月 7 日被杀并运往加沙的五名以色列人的尸体。 ■ 内塔尼亚胡向国会发表的讲话中没有提及“协议”或“停火”。 ■ 以色列推迟卡塔尔会谈；官员表示，拜登和内塔尼亚胡正在就加沙协议进行讨论以色列从东方</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 02:28:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article-live/gaza-truce-talks-in-closing-stages-senior-u-s-official-says-israeli-source-gaps-remain/00000190-e7ae-d469-a39d-e7bfcb150000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡在国会的空洞“胜利”：在演讲中获胜，在战争中失败</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-hollow-triumph-in-congress-winning-in-speeches-losing-in-wars/00000190-e668-d8b8-a59a-eefeb7e90000</link><description>哈斯巴拉的陈词滥调、空洞的承诺、兴高采烈的共和党人：内塔尼亚胡的讲话脱离了战时现实 — — 也脱离了以色列人</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 21:20:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-hollow-triumph-in-congress-winning-in-speeches-losing-in-wars/00000190-e668-d8b8-a59a-eefeb7e90000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡前往华盛顿并不是为了结束加沙战争。他去寻找延长时间的方法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-didnt-go-to-washington-to-end-gaza-war-he-went-to-get-the-means-to-prolong-it/00000190-e68a-d6e6-afde-e6df058e0000</link><description>虽然更多的以色列人质尸体被发现，内塔尼亚胡不仅寻求美国武器的支持，而且还寻求以色列对加沙地带的永久控制</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 21:18:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-didnt-go-to-washington-to-end-gaza-war-he-went-to-get-the-means-to-prolong-it/00000190-e68a-d6e6-afde-e6df058e0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡在国会表示，以色列不会重新安置加沙，抨击校园抗议者是伊朗“有用的白痴”，并呼吁建立区域联盟</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-says-israel-wont-resettle-gaza-campus-protesters-are-irans-useful-idiots/00000190-e64a-d541-adbc-fffa7c6e0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡在国会演讲中呼吁美国继续武装以色列，以便以色列能够“更快地完成任务”，但没有提及加沙停火和人质协议。六名人质亲属因抗议被带出会议厅并被捕</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 21:04:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-says-israel-wont-resettle-gaza-campus-protesters-are-irans-useful-idiots/00000190-e64a-d541-adbc-fffa7c6e0000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日，以色列军队在汗尤尼斯行动中找到了被带到加沙的五名以色列人的尸体</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/israel-recovers-body-of-maya-goren-kidnapped-on-oct-7-and-killed-in-captivity/00000190-e656-d8b8-a59a-eede01260000</link><description>以色列军队表示，本周在汗尤尼斯发动的突袭行动的主要目标之一是打捞人质尸体，据报道，那里有 70 名巴勒斯坦人被杀。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 20:16:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/israel-recovers-body-of-maya-goren-kidnapped-on-oct-7-and-killed-in-captivity/00000190-e656-d8b8-a59a-eede01260000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔推动立法让他控制以色列国民警卫队</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-pushes-legislation-giving-him-control-over-israels-national-guard/00000190-e55c-d149-afbb-ef5dc7080000</link><description>一位知情人士告诉《国土报》，极右翼国家安全部长的决议草案“试图建立一支由他控制的安全部队”</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 19:49:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-pushes-legislation-giving-him-control-over-israels-national-guard/00000190-e55c-d149-afbb-ef5dc7080000</guid></item><item><title>以色列推迟卡塔尔会谈；官员表示，等待拜登和内塔尼亚胡就加沙协议进行讨论后离开</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-delays-qatar-talks-departure-awaits-biden-netanyahu-discussion-on-gaza-deal/00000190-e5c9-d322-a1df-efff518b0000</link><description>一名官员表示，拜登和内塔尼亚胡之间的会面对于设定人质交易的参数至关重要 ■ 人质的母亲指责总理出于个人利益而阻止交易</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 17:54:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-delays-qatar-talks-departure-awaits-biden-netanyahu-discussion-on-gaza-deal/00000190-e5c9-d322-a1df-efff518b0000</guid></item><item><title>“内塔尼亚胡是战犯”：以色列总理在国会发表讲话，数千人在美国国会大厦外抗议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/thousands-protest-outside-u-s-capitol-as-israeli-pm-addresses-congress/00000190-e5c1-d149-afbb-efc5bd570000</link><description>在内塔尼亚胡总理向国会发表讲话之前，已部署了大量警察部队。早些时候，示威者试图阻止以色列总理前往国会山的车队，并在他的酒店外悬挂巴勒斯坦国旗</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 17:53:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/thousands-protest-outside-u-s-capitol-as-israeli-pm-addresses-congress/00000190-e5c1-d149-afbb-efc5bd570000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡会见美国福音派领袖，称以色列“没有更好的朋友”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-meets-u-s-evangelical-leaders-says-israel-has-no-better-friends/00000190-e5af-d322-a1df-efff46170000</link><description>以色列总理会见了几位信仰领袖，其中包括约翰·哈吉牧师，他在活动中表示基督徒“对我们政府对待犹太人民的方式感到震惊”</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 17:41:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-meets-u-s-evangelical-leaders-says-israel-has-no-better-friends/00000190-e5af-d322-a1df-efff46170000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于战争状态，第 292 天：甘茨说，自上次休战提议以来，四分之一的活着的人质死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-292-quarter-of-hostages-died-since-last-truce-proposal-gantz-says/00000190-e5ad-d322-a1df-efff0d3d0001</link><description>总理内塔尼亚胡在国会联席会议上发表讲话，反对议员的强烈抗议和抵制 ■ 以色列将原定于周四前往卡塔尔的代表团推迟到下周 ■ 以色列将 250 名加沙伤病员疏散到阿联酋接受治疗 ■ 真主党发布了以色列人的无人机镜头空军基地 ■ 战争进入 292 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 17:03:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-292-quarter-of-hostages-died-since-last-truce-proposal-gantz-says/00000190-e5ad-d322-a1df-efff0d3d0001</guid></item><item><title>100年前想要皈依犹太教的贝都因部落后来怎么样了？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/what-had-happened-to-the-bedouin-tribe-that-wanted-to-convert-to-judaism-100-years-ago/00000190-e49c-dab4-afb9-f7fcf7e60000</link><description>整整一个世纪前，《国土报》报道了加利利的一个部落寻求皈依。 1948年犹太人就是这样对待它的</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 16:06:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/what-had-happened-to-the-bedouin-tribe-that-wanted-to-convert-to-judaism-100-years-ago/00000190-e49c-dab4-afb9-f7fcf7e60000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡即将在国会发表讲话，他面临着最可怕的噩梦：无关紧要</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/set-to-address-congress-netanyahu-faces-his-worst-nightmare-irrelevancy/00000190-e425-d363-abbf-eeaf81ca0000</link><description>总理本打算将内塔尼亚胡的讲话视为美以关系的里程碑时刻，但内塔尼亚胡的讲话将被深深分裂、有些敌对、几乎完全心烦意乱的听众听到</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 14:47:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/set-to-address-congress-netanyahu-faces-his-worst-nightmare-irrelevancy/00000190-e425-d363-abbf-eeaf81ca0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列极右翼部长本-格维尔支持特朗普，称拜登退出“没有重大损失”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/israels-far-right-minister-ben-gvir-endorses-trump-says-biden-bowing-out-no-big-loss/00000190-e4c5-d469-a39d-e4d7a8270000</link><description>这位极右翼部长在接受彭博社采访时表示，“内阁部长应该保持中立，但在拜登之后就不可能做到这一点”，并表示“在特朗普的领导下，必须击败敌人会更加清楚”</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 13:47:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/israels-far-right-minister-ben-gvir-endorses-trump-says-biden-bowing-out-no-big-loss/00000190-e4c5-d469-a39d-e4d7a8270000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡与本格维尔会谈，将极右翼部长加入新的战争论坛，国防部长谴责该计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/israels-defense-chief-dont-let-pyromaniac-ben-gvir-be-part-of-new-war-cabinet/00000190-e477-d566-adfa-ef77edad0000</link><description>极右翼国家安全部长本-格维尔要求总理内塔尼亚胡将他纳入就战争做出战略决策的有限论坛中。国防部长约阿夫·加兰特强烈反对这一想法，称本格维尔“试图点燃中东”</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 12:17:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/israels-defense-chief-dont-let-pyromaniac-ben-gvir-be-part-of-new-war-cabinet/00000190-e477-d566-adfa-ef77edad0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人面临新的恐惧：无人机袭击期间住在高楼里</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/new-fear-unlocked-for-israelis-living-in-high-rises-during-drone-attacks/00000190-df21-d566-adfa-ff23b2010000</link><description>当一架无人机击中以色列高层建筑时，楼上居民只能孤军奋战：上周胡塞武装袭击特拉维夫，这对一个摩天大楼之国来说是个坏兆头，因为这个国家没有办法保护他们</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 10:51:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/new-fear-unlocked-for-israelis-living-in-high-rises-during-drone-attacks/00000190-df21-d566-adfa-ff23b2010000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政界人士认为内塔尼亚胡赞成达成协议，但将避免在国会演讲中这么说</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/israeli-politicians-think-netanyahu-favors-deal-but-will-avoid-saying-so-in-speech/00000190-e3ee-d9bf-a195-e7ee3a6a0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡访问期间民主党的回避强化了他和特朗普的说法，因为他们寻求重建关系。尽管所有人的目光都集中在总理的讲话上，但很少有人注意到司法政变的卷土重来</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 10:41:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/israeli-politicians-think-netanyahu-favors-deal-but-will-avoid-saying-so-in-speech/00000190-e3ee-d9bf-a195-e7ee3a6a0000</guid></item><item><title>一场失败的比赛：加沙战争导致海外球员远离以色列体育遭受干旱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-07-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-losing-game-israeli-sports-suffers-drought-as-gaza-war-sees-overseas-players-stay-away/00000190-d515-dbb4-a7d2-df1f92af0000</link><description>运动员不敢与以色列队签约，他们的父母拒绝让他们来，经纪人也要求更多的钱。只有那些已经在以色列打过球的人才准备好本赛季在这里打球——除了财力雄厚的三巨头篮球俱乐部</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 10:32:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-07-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-losing-game-israeli-sports-suffers-drought-as-gaza-war-sees-overseas-players-stay-away/00000190-d515-dbb4-a7d2-df1f92af0000</guid></item></channel></rss>